import React from 'react'
import {BrowserRouter as Router } from "react-router-dom"

import Header from './Components/Header'
import HomeScreen from './Screens/HomeScreen'

function App() {
  return (
  <>

  <Header/>
  <main>
    <HomeScreen/> 
  </main>
  <Footer/>

  </>

  )
}

export default App
